---

---

<section
  class="w-full bg-transparent relative overflow-hidden"
  data-parallax-section
  data-parallax-depth="0.04"
>
  <!-- Old manifesto: logo left (half visible), repetitive text + signature right -->
  <div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 relative z-10 mb-16 justify-center items-center flex flex-col">
        
    <h2
    class="text-white text-3xl w-full text-start md:w-1/3  leading-tight"
  >
    What is <span class="relative inline-block font-bold text-white">
      Devlabs ?
     
    </span>
 
  </h2>

    <p
          class="md:w-1/3 text-white text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed whitespace-pre-line text-start"
        >
          We've poured our hearts into building
          something bigger than an organization -

          a home for early builders working on ideas that start small but dream big.

          Ideas born in dorm rooms. In basements. In garages.

          Those small ideas?
          They're the ones we help turn into something real.

          For years, we've worked to build DevLabs into a space where young founders feel unstoppable.
          Because when you're young, the sky isn't the limit - it's just the beginning.

          The fastest way to grow is feel the energy of a room full of people who are just as crazy enough to try.

          DevLabs is on a mission to become the launchpad for the next 100 student startups.

          From hackathons to Arizona's first hacker house.
          From $0 in funding to over $100,000 invested in builders.

          We've come a long way. But we're just getting started.

          Welcome to DevLabs, early bird.
          You're about to have the ride of your life.

          Build. Ship. Repeat.
        </p>
        <div
          class="mt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-8"
        >
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <img
              src="/dhanush_sign.png"
              alt="Dhanush signature"
              loading="lazy"
              class="h-10 sm:h-12 w-auto opacity-90 mt-4"
            />
            <p class="text-sm">Dhanush Vardhan</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <img
              src="/bhoomi_sign.png"
              alt="Bhoomi signature"
              loading="lazy"
              class="h-10 sm:h-12 w-auto opacity-90 invert"
            />
            <p class="text-sm">Bhoomi Sanjay Sahajsinghani</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
 
  <!-- Theme background overlay (soft, no hard edges) -->
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="h-[200px] absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-[#151413]/10 to-[#151413]/25"
  >
  </div>

  <!-- Full-width layout with only side padding "margin" -->
  <div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-12 relative z-10">
    <div class="manifesto-frame relative w-full border border-white/15">
      <!-- Top segmented bar -->
      <div
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-12 border-b border-white/15 flex"
      >
        <div class="w-[28%] bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/25 to-white/5">
        </div>
        <div class="w-[26%] bg-gradient-to-r from-white/5 to-orange-400/15">
        </div>
        <div
          class="flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-white/5 via-white/10 to-orange-500/20"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="w-[12%] bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-white/5">
        </div>

        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-between px-6 text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-white/70"
        >
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">The biggest misconceptions</span>
          <span class="text-white/70">build.ship.repeat</span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">We are builders</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom segmented bar -->
      <div
        class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-12 border-t border-white/15 flex"
      >
        <div class="w-[33%] bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/22 to-transparent">
        </div>
        <div
          class="w-[34%] bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[#151413]/45 to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-orange-500/18">
        </div>

        <div
          class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-between px-6 text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-white/75"
        >
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">Go Big or Get Hired</span>
          <span class="hidden sm:inline">We are builders</span>
          <span class="text-white/65">build.ship.repeat</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Side rails -->
      <div
        class="absolute left-0 top-12 bottom-12 w-12 border-r border-white/15"
      >
        <div
          class="h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-orange-500/25 via-white/5 to-transparent"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center px-1">
          <span
            class="manifesto-vert text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-white/70"
          >
            build.ship.repeat
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div
        class="absolute right-0 top-12 bottom-12 w-12 border-l border-white/15"
      >
        <div
          class="h-full bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 via-white/5 to-orange-500/10"
        >
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center px-1">
          <span
            class="manifesto-vert text-[10px] tracking-[0.22em] uppercase text-white/70"
          >
            build.ship.repeat
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Inner panel -->
      <div class="px-6 sm:px-10 py-8 sm:py-10">
        <div
          class="relative bg-[#151413]/90 border border-white/15 overflow-hidden"
        >
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-white/15"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-px bg-white/15"></div>

          <!-- Corner stars (left star: half visible, right half only) -->
          <img
            src="/star.svg"
            alt=""
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 translate-x-1/3 translate-y-1/2 sm:right-auto sm:bottom-auto sm:left-0 sm:-translate-x-1/2 sm:-top-24 w-[26rem] sm:w-[32rem] md:w-[36rem] opacity-50 pointer-events-none select-none z-0 rotate-[20deg]"
          />
          <img
            src="/star.svg"
            alt=""
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="absolute right-0 top-0 translate-x-1/3 -translate-y-1/2 w-60 sm:w-72 md:w-80 rotate-[8deg] opacity-50 pointer-events-none select-none z-0"
          />

          <!-- Center watermark logo -->
          <img
            src="/logo.png"
            alt=""
            aria-hidden="true"
            class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-20 sm:w-24 md:w-28 h-auto pointer-events-none opacity-90 select-none z-[1]"
          />

          <!-- Copy (matches reference positioning) -->
          <div
            class="relative z-10 px-6 sm:px-10 md:px-12 py-10 sm:py-12 md:py-14"
          >
            <!-- All sizes: pinned corners inside the box -->
            <div
              class="relative w-full min-h-[210px] sm:min-h-[230px] md:min-h-[220px]"
            >
              <!-- Left block (top-left) -->
              <div
                class="absolute top-[5px] left-[5px] max-w-[75%] sm:max-w-xl text-left"
              >
                <p
                  class="text-white text-lg sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-tight"
                >
                  We believe the best way
                </p>

                <!-- Keep “to learn is to” aligned to top vs the big word -->
                <div class="flex flex-wrap items-start gap-x-3 gap-y-1">
                  <p
                    class="text-white text-lg sm:text-2xl md:text-3xl leading-tight"
                  >
                    to learn is to
                  </p>
                  <span
                    class="manifesto-emphasis text-4xl sm:text-6xl md:text-7xl leading-none text-white"
                    style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;"
                    >build</span
                  >
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Right block (bottom-right) -->
              <div
                class="absolute bottom-[5px] right-[5px] flex flex-col items-end text-right max-w-[80%] sm:max-w-xl"
              >
                <p
                  class="text-white/95 text-base sm:text-xl md:text-2xl leading-tight"
                >
                  *Devlabs is a place to
                </p>
                <p
                  class="manifesto-emphasis text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl leading-none mt-2 text-white"
                  style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;"
                >
                  build.ship.repeat
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .manifesto-vert {
    writing-mode: vertical-rl;
    transform: rotate(180deg);
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .manifesto-frame {
    box-shadow:
      0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06),
      0 30px 120px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.65),
      0 0 80px rgba(249, 115, 22, 0.08);
  }

  .manifesto-emphasis {
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    display: inline-block;
  }
</style>
